}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "48DNUR09.0GB" is silkscreened on the board. {{see also|Unex|Wistron NeWeb}}
===Features=== Features 802.11n dual-band in flexible 4-Pin USB 2.0 header with on-board U.FL connectors, DNUR-S2 delivers up to 300Mbps data rate and easily bring quality-consistent Wi-Fi to the USB-equipped system with external Wi-Fi antennas.
*802.11abgn dual-band USB module :with on-board U.FL connectors :Flexible USB 2.0 4-pin header :Data rate: up to 300Mbps
